text: Ganar Cádiz en Común (Spanish for Winning Cádiz in Common) is an electoral alliance formed by United Left/The Greens–Assembly for Andalusia, Equo and Citizens for Cádiz to contest the 2015 Cádiz municipal election. ==Member parties== *United Left/The Greens–Assembly for Andalusia (IULV–CA) *Equo (eQuo) *Citizens for Cádiz (CPCAD) ==Electoral performance== ===City Council of Cádiz=== {| class="wikitable" style="font-size:98%;" |- ! width="65" rowspan="2"| Date ! colspan="3"| Votes ! colspan="2"| Seats ! rowspan="2"| Status ! rowspan="2"| Size |- ! width="75"| # ! % ! ±pp ! # ! ± |- ! 2015 | 5,487 | 8.4% | –1.7 | style="text-align:center;"| | 10px1 | style="background- color:#fcc;"| Opposition | 4th |} ==References== Category:Political parties in Andalusia Category:Political parties established in 2015 Category:Political party alliances in Spain
